#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.quantile.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.quantile"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:1 of
msgid "Return value at the given quantile."
msgstr "返回给定分位数处的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:3 of
msgid "0 <= q <= 1, the quantile(s) to compute."
msgstr "0 <= q <= 1，要计算的分位数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:5 of
msgid ""
"This optional parameter specifies the interpolation method to use, when "
"the desired quantile lies between two data points `i` and `j`:      * "
"linear: `i + (j - i) * fraction`, where `fraction` is the       "
"fractional part of the index surrounded by `i` and `j`.     * lower: `i`."
"     * higher: `j`.     * nearest: `i` or `j` whichever is nearest.     *"
" midpoint: (`i` + `j`) / 2."
msgstr ""
"此可选参数指定当所需的分位数位于两个数据点 `i` 和 `j` 之间时使用的插值"
"方法：      * linear: `i + (j - i) * fraction`，其中 `fraction` 是索引在 "
"`i` 和 `j` 之间的分数部分。     * lower: `i`。     * higher: `j`。     * "
"nearest: 最接近的 `i` 或 `j`。     * midpoint: (`i` + `j`) / 2。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:5 of
msgid ""
"This optional parameter specifies the interpolation method to use, when "
"the desired quantile lies between two data points `i` and `j`:"
msgstr ""
"此可选参数指定当所需分位数位于两个数据点 `i` 和 `j` 之间时要使用的插值"
"方法："

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:8 of
msgid ""
"linear: `i + (j - i) * fraction`, where `fraction` is the fractional part"
" of the index surrounded by `i` and `j`."
msgstr ""
"linear: `i + (j - i) * fraction`，其中 `fraction` 是由 `i` 和 `j` 包围的"
"索引的小数部分。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:10 of
msgid "lower: `i`."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:11 of
msgid "higher: `j`."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:12 of
msgid "nearest: `i` or `j` whichever is nearest."
msgstr "nearest: `i` 或 `j` 中最近的一个。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:13 of
msgid "midpoint: (`i` + `j`) / 2."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:16 of
msgid ""
"If ``q`` is an array or a tensor, a Series will be returned where the "
"index is ``q`` and the values are the quantiles, otherwise a float will "
"be returned."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``q`` 是数组或张量，则返回一个 Series，其索引为 ``q``，值为分位数；"
"否则返回一个浮点数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.series_quantile:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`core.window.Rolling.quantile`, :py:obj:`numpy.percentile`"
msgstr ""

